      <title>随着更广泛战争的风险增加，布林肯再次前往中东</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/blinken-is-off-to-mideast-again-as-risk-of-wider-war-increases</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尽管从红海到黎巴嫩的紧张局势不断升级，美国国务卿安东尼·布林肯本周将第四次访问中东，这是自 10 月 7 日以色列遇袭以来，美国继续努力避免更广泛的地区冲突。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/blinken-is-off-to-mideast-again-as-risk-of-wider-war-increases</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 17:42:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>拜登太阳能关税假期受到挑战，增加了新的行业风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/biden-solar-tariff-holiday-challenged-adding-new-industry-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[两家美国太阳能制造商对拜登政府在 6 月初暂停对部分从东南亚进口的电池板征收关税的决定提出质疑，这给已经面临供应链障碍的行业带来了新的风险。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/biden-solar-tariff-holiday-challenged-adding-new-industry-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 17:35:34 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>伊斯兰国声称对伊朗致命爆炸事件负责</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/islamic-state-claims-responsibility-for-deadly-iran-blasts</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊斯兰国声称对周三在伊朗发生的袭击事件负责，该袭击造成近 100 人死亡，并有可能进一步加剧中东紧张局势。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/islamic-state-claims-responsibility-for-deadly-iran-blasts</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 17:13:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>丹格特被卷入尼日利亚对前央​​行行长的调查</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/dangote-dragged-into-nigeria-probe-of-ex-central-bank-chief</link>
      <description><![CDATA[尼日利亚反腐败官员参观了由亿万富翁阿里科·丹格特控制的丹格特工业有限公司的办公室，这是对该国央行前行长戈德温·埃梅菲勒正在进行的调查的一部分。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/dangote-dragged-into-nigeria-probe-of-ex-central-bank-chief</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 16:58:04 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国立法者考虑为企业和儿童制定 1000 亿美元税收协议</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/us-business-child-tax-break-deal-percolating-on-capitol-hill</link>
      <description><![CDATA[渴望看到国会恢复过期的研究和投资税收减免的企业有理由乐观地认为，协议最早可能在本月达成。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/us-business-child-tax-break-deal-percolating-on-capitol-hill</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 16:54:57 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国海军上将称，胡塞武装红海袭击没有减弱的迹象</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/houthi-red-sea-attacks-show-no-sign-of-abating-us-admiral-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国海军司令称，美国领导的红海部队在不到一个月的时间里击落了伊朗支持的也门胡塞武装发射的19架无人机和导弹，但没有迹象表明武装分子会后退。中东说。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/houthi-red-sea-attacks-show-no-sign-of-abating-us-admiral-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 16:53:17 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>民主党人称特朗普酒店在总统任期内获得了外国资金</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/trump-hotels-made-millions-from-foreign-governments-during-term</link>
      <description><![CDATA[根据众议院民主党人的一份报告，唐纳德·特朗普 (Donald Trump) 旗下的酒店在他担任总统期间从外国政府及其代表那里获得了至少 780 万美元的付款。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/trump-hotels-made-millions-from-foreign-governments-during-term</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 16:51:54 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>科威特任命哈佛毕业的经济学家、外交官为新总理</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/kuwait-taps-harvard-educated-economist-diplomat-as-new-premier</link>
      <description><![CDATA[科威特统治者任命谢赫·穆罕默德·萨巴赫·萨利姆·萨巴赫为该国新首相，希望这位 68 岁的哈佛大学经济学博士学位获得者制定一条可能包括经济发展在内的新路线。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/kuwait-taps-harvard-educated-economist-diplomat-as-new-premier</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 16:35:35 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>特朗普希望特别检察官杰克·史密斯在 1 月 6 日藐视法庭案中被关押</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/trump-wants-jack-smith-held-in-contempt-of-court-in-jan-6-case</link>
      <description><![CDATA[唐纳德·特朗普指责特别检察官杰克·史密斯违反了法院命令，该命令搁置了对前总统的选举干涉诉讼，而他对推翻他的豁免权辩护的裁决提出了上诉。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/trump-wants-jack-smith-held-in-contempt-of-court-in-jan-6-case</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 15:11:55 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>由于霍乱死亡人数激增，赞比亚推迟了学年开始时间</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/zambia-delays-start-of-school-year-as-cholera-deaths-rise</link>
      <description><![CDATA[随着赞比亚霍乱死亡人数不断攀升，赞比亚将学年开学推迟了三周，与 2018 年 1 月采取的措施相呼应。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-01-04/zambia-delays-start-of-school-year-as-cholera-deaths-rise</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 04 Jan 2024 12:50:05 GMT</pubDate>
